The rugs’ vision represents the natural continuation of a 
process of innovation.
Transforming a product, famously recognized as an 
expression of craftsmanship, into art takes over living 
spaces and becomes practical: this is the aim of the experimentation.
Entirely handmade with spun fabrics, these rugs take over 
the design language, beyond the limits of the frames of the 
paintings from which they are inspired.
